attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

object.customQuery:
select
	row_id,
	acx_coverage_item_row_id,
	acx_coverage_item_row_md5checksum,
	acx_coverage_item_row_effective_end_datetime 
from
	$$staging_schema.acx_coverage_item
where
	acx_coverage_item_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
order by system_id, cmm_container ;
